ate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/100-hebrew-university-faculty-protest-suspension-of-scholar-alleging-israeli-gaza-genocide/0000018e-3993-d3fc-adff-b9b383330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学是否应该解雇一名称哈马斯暴行是“谎言”的学者？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</link><description>在这一点上，如果所有这些受惊的大学管理部门和愤怒的抵制者都得逞，校园里唯一剩下的争论将是关于自助餐厅的选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 21:13:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-13/ty-article/.highlight/should-an-israeli-university-fire-an-academic-who-said-hamas-atrocities-are-lies/0000018e-38e7-d21d-a3ef-3be7aa4f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府攻击科学的另一个目标：享誉世界的火山研究所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/another-target-of-the-israeli-governments-war-on-science-the-acclaimed-volcani-institute/0000018e-3884-d2fd-a1fe-3df56d6d0000</link><description>以色列的粮食安全取决于火山研究所在农业领域所做的开创性工作。预算削减表明以色列政府优先考虑投资过去，而不是未来</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 20:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/another-target-of-the-israeli-governments-war-on-science-the-acclaimed-volcani-institute/0000018e-3884-d2fd-a1fe-3df56d6d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡没有告诉拜登有关以色列人和加沙战争的全部真相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡告诉拜登和 AIPAC，以色列人绝大多数支持他的战时政策，而忽略了公众对他的领导力和加沙“全面胜利”承诺的信心下降。问题是以色列人何时以及是否会开始呼吁结束战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军最高指挥官在呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于他们的士兵”后接受质询</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</link><description>双桅船。丹·戈德福斯将军呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于预备役军人，他们不关心自己来自哪一方，并肩作战”，并“确保每个人都参与其中”，但这一呼吁并未得到他的上级指挥官的批准。他向加沙地带以外的媒体发表的声明</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</guid></item></channel></rss>